{"tid":831622,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係lihkg share/ 求share telegram 嘅入一入來","createTime":"2018-09-22T06:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T06:58:50.000Z","uid":62286,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b29c775d99d3ca88eafe22fd536933ae93fa598","tid":831622,"uid":62286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"就咁嘅<br />\n<br />\n你老母閪人地整個討論區岀來，就係俾人係依一個平台上面暢談，分享大家對世事不同嘅想法，意見，以至source, link,圖，甚至係av嘅code, seed.<br />\n<br />\n唔撚知邊啲撚樣閪樣柒頭皮帶壞個風氣，有好嘢又叫人留tg，先同人傾落去，先分享自己嘅source俾人。甚至樓主無叫人留tg，都一大班傻尻自己留tg。<br />\n<br />\n見到有丁圖流岀又留tg，想要啲女IG又留tg，知邊度有平貨買又留tg，想講某U或某圈子嘅是非又留tg，想呃蝦條又留tg<br />\n<br />\n不如索性叫lihkg做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Telegram轉介平台</span>啦<br />\n<br />\n你可以話唔想俾街外人知太多，所以就tg講。其實可以用會員加密。 好啦，我當會有解密狗，但其實你啲source，你啲消息，係tg俾人根本等同俾全世界人睇，你點知對方咩人，對方會同咩人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好再留telegram/ 叫人留telegram, 有咩就依度lihkg講，唔敢俾人知嘅就連telegram 都唔好講</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f64f0451ccf7c33384961989879eeb0c30f34094","tid":831622,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"樓主你講得好有道理<br />\n<br />\n不如留低tg再傾"},{"pid":"1d7b31df55766063c03353f7f099b97f232405b0","tid":831622,"uid":62286,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f64f0451ccf7c33384961989879eeb0c30f34094","tid":831622,"uid":32577,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"樓主你講得好有道理<br />\n<br />\n不如留低tg再傾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4cc131090ce8df66ecfba401cb2d1f1fd106bd","tid":831622,"uid":16468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢個問題好有討論價值<br />\n不如開個tg 谷一齊研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd041702af041bf398072645c2285c4b8d248e86","t